2017-03-15 Release 1.0.0
- [WARNING] THIS RELEASE DROPS SUPPORT FOR PUPPET 3
- Add precreate option and the ability to provide extra arguments to adjoin
- Add self-serve join option
- Move to data-in-modules paradigm
2016-10-20 Release 0.3.0
- add support for specifying zones and containers during join
- centrifydc_line type converts all value param settings to strings
2016-05-13 Release 0.2.0
- add configurable flush and reload cronjob
- add ability to set Express license
- manage sshd service enable and ensure parameters independently
2015-10-15 Release 0.1.0
- initial Puppet Forge release
